subject_information.comments: It was disappointing that I wasn't able to play because my partner disconnected. Thank you for compensating it, but I would have enjoyed being able to come back and attempt it with a new partner.
subject_information.problems: Yes: "Oops! It looks like your partner lost their connection!"
subject_information.strategy: No strategy. I was informed that my partner lost connection, and that I should complete this survey and submit the hit anyway.
